description: The Sawtooth X Low Waterproof has all the bells and whistles of the non-waterproof version, but with the added benefit of our B-DRY waterproof and breathable technology. While the new Sawtooth X has refined styling, it retains the Cordura vents that help promote breathability and make it recognizably a Sawtooth. But your feet will recognize it as a Sawtooth first and foremost.
name: Oboz Sawtooth X Low B-Dry - Mens
